title: Emprox hits Oceania 2018
body:
Saying goodbye to the underdogs of the last split known as Lynx 2017 was hard but understandable.

Emprox now takes their torch and burns brighter in their name with a new brand, new outlook and new faces that are looking to be the next rising team in Oceania within the Oceanic Challenger Series.

Bold statements? Yea we know, only the brave and the bold get to challenge the kings and this time around we are coming for the ones at the top. 

OPL we are on our way!
